des:
This skill randomly serves up original verse, such as:

 Crows are not hipsters
 Avocados will kill them
 No crows for Brooklyn.

EXAMPLE PHRASES

You can call up a haiku by saying 

“Alexa, open Haiku Reader”

“Alexa, ask Haiku Reader to tell me a haiku”

Or even

“Alexa, ask Haiku Reader to amuse me."
